summary: An ordinance repealing Ordinance No. 24998 entitled: "An ordinance authorizing and directing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of 21st Avenue South from Hanford Street to Rainier Avenue et al, in the City of Seattle, by grading and curbing the same, etc, under Ordinance No. 20428 creating Local Improvement District No. 2023, prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement."
